<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bloom-n">bloom <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bluːm/    美 /bluːm/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>花；开花：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What beautiful blooms! 
多漂亮的花啊！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>come into bloom 
开花</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-full-bloom">in (full) bloom</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(盛) 开着花：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The roses are in full bloom now. 
玫瑰盛开着。</p></div></div>